How did we end up so different?

1019
01:17:41,440 --> 01:17:42,910
Hmm? Hmm?

1020
01:17:43,280 --> 01:17:44,650
Sit down!

1021
01:17:45,000 --> 01:17:46,230
[HECTOR HARRUMPHS]

1022
01:17:47,040 --> 01:17:48,090
Now...

1023
01:17:50,360 --> 01:17:51,370
.. how's Carol?

1024
01:17:53,600 --> 01:17:54,830
-That came out wrong.
-Please.

1025
01:17:55,160 --> 01:17:56,809
HAL: I've made mistakes--
-Look, Hal--

1026
01:17:57,200 --> 01:17:59,200
I feel bad for you, really. Good night.

1027
01:17:59,640 --> 01:18:02,170
[HECTOR PANTING]

1028
01:18:05,080 --> 01:18:08,660
You're just as much of a failure
as I was.

1029
01:18:10,400 --> 01:18:11,799
And just as afraid.

1030
01:18:13,160 --> 01:18:15,190
Well...

1031
01:18:16,160 --> 01:18:18,050
.. 1 used to fight my fear.

1032
01:18:21,920 --> 01:18:25,430
But now that I've tasted
its true power...

1033
01:18:29,360 --> 01:18:31,110
..l'll never go back.

1034
01:18:31,520 --> 01:18:34,190
[YELLING]

1035
01:18:37,880 --> 01:18:38,960
[SCREAMING]

1036
01:18:39,520 --> 01:18:41,170
HAL:
No!

1037
01:18:48,720 --> 01:18:51,250
[GRUNTING]

1038
01:18:54,440 --> 01:18:55,669
[YELLING]

1039
01:19:00,280 --> 01:19:03,330
You wear the ring of the Lantern
that imprisoned me.

1040
01:19:04,640 --> 01:19:06,710
You will suffer the same fate.

1041
01:19:07,160 --> 01:19:09,970
Once I have devoured your world...

1042
01:19:10,520 --> 01:19:12,480
fd will have all the strength I need...

1043
01:19:12,920 --> 01:19:16,180
..to defeat the Corps
and destroy the Guardians.

1044
01:19:20,640 --> 01:19:23,170
[HECTOR YELLING]

1045
01:19:26,240 --> 01:19:28,769
[SCREAMING]

1046
01:19:47,680 --> 01:19:48,800
TOM:
Let me get this straight.

1047
01:19:49,120 --> 01:19:51,960
This thing that's out there attacking
planets is connected to Hector?

1048
01:19:52,520 --> 01:19:54,690
Somehow it infected him
after it killed Abin Sur.

1049
01:19:55,160 --> 01:19:58,710
-Well, you're just gonna have to stop it.
-Oh, I'm just gonna have to stop it, huh?

1050
01:19:59,360 --> 01:20:00,759
Well, I tried that and I failed.

1051
01:20:01,120 --> 01:20:03,930
And the senator died.
I told you, the ring made a mistake.

1052
01:20:04,480 --> 01:20:06,730
Wait, go back.
How did the ring make a mistake?

1053
01:20:07,200 --> 01:20:11,380
The one thing that a Green Lantern
is supposed to be is fearless.

1054
01:20:12,480 --> 01:20:15,110
Fearless is the job description.

1055
01:20:16,080 --> 01:20:16,950
That isn't me.

1056
01:20:17,240 --> 01:20:19,240
So you're just gonna walk away again?

1057
01:20:19,680 --> 01:20:22,980
Explain this to me, Hal.
Please explain to me just once, why.

1058
01:20:23,600 --> 01:20:25,070
Because I'm afraid!

1059
01:20:41,400 --> 01:20:43,120
You don't think your dad
ever felt afraid?

1060
01:20:44,600 --> 01:20:46,140
If he did,
he figured out some way to beat it.

1061
01:20:46,520 --> 01:20:48,800
Yeah, well, there's a word for that:

1062
01:20:49,440 --> 01:20:50,740
Courage.

1063
01:20:57,560 --> 01:21:00,680
They said that the ring wouldn't have
chosen me if it didn't see something.

1064
01:21:02,080 --> 01:21:04,850
Something I don't see. Yet.

1065
01:21:08,800 --> 01:21:09,960
I see it.

1066
01:21:11,400 --> 01:21:13,049
l always have.

1067
01:21:14,160 --> 01:21:16,190
The ring didn't see
that you were fearless.

1068
01:21:16,640 --> 01:21:19,450
It saw that you had the ability
to overcome fear.

1069
01:21:20,560 --> 01:21:22,590
It saw that you're courageous.

1070
01:21:25,920 --> 01:21:27,040
Which you are.

1071
01:21:28,000 --> 01:21:29,120
Just like your dad.

1072
01:21:33,760 --> 01:21:36,290
[GRUNTING]

1073
01:21:37,600 --> 01:21:39,880
PARALLAX:
The Lantern is a threat.

1074
01:21:41,040 --> 01:21:42,970
Eliminate him.

1075
01:22:15,840 --> 01:22:17,630
SINESTRO:
Our new weapon is ready.

1076
01:22:18,560 --> 01:22:19,960
Once I've mastered its power...

1077
01:22:20,800 --> 01:22:23,050
I'll begin training the Corps
to do the same.

1078
01:22:24,640 --> 01:22:26,460
Though Earth will be lost...

1079
01:22:27,120 --> 01:22:30,559
.. we'll be ready to make a stand against
Parallax before it reaches Oa.

1080
01:22:31,200 --> 01:22:32,599
Then the power of the enemy
will be ours.

1081
01:22:32,960 --> 01:22:34,430
HAL:
At what cost?

1082
01:22:37,280 --> 01:22:39,530
SINESTRO: You dare enter this chamber?
-I need your help.

1083
01:22:41,400 --> 01:22:43,259
You gotta help me save my world.

1084
01:22:51,040 --> 01:22:55,390
I know that humans aren't
the strongest species, or the smartest.

1085
01:22:57,360 --> 01:22:59,110
We're young, we have a lot to learn.

1086
01:23:00,040 --> 01:23:01,120
But we're worth saving.

1087
01:23:09,640 --> 01:23:11,570
This new weapon of yours,
you can't use it.

1088
01:23:12,040 --> 01:23:14,070
Once you cross that line,
once you've given in to fear...

1089
01:23:14,520 --> 01:23:16,270
.- you'll never go back. I've seen it.

1090
01:23:17,720 --> 01:23:20,110
Look, I know right now you're afraid.

1091
01:23:20,600 --> 01:23:22,560
You dare accuse the Guardians
of feeling fear?

1092
01:23:23,000 --> 01:23:24,080
Yes, I do.

1093
01:23:24,400 --> 01:23:26,219
That's exactly why Parallax
is beating you...

1094
01:23:26,640 --> 01:23:28,810
.. because you're afraid
to even admit you're afraid.

1095
01:23:29,280 --> 01:23:30,610
I know.

1096
01:23:31,200 --> 01:23:32,849
I spent my entire life doing it.

1097
01:23:34,240 --> 01:23:36,410
You know, we have a saying on Earth.

1098
01:23:36,880 --> 01:23:39,020
We say, "I'm only human."

1099
01:23:40,960 --> 01:23:44,010
We say it because we're vulnerable,
we say it because we know we're afraid.

1100
01:23:44,600 --> 01:23:46,390
It doesn't mean we're weak.

1101
01:23:48,800 --> 01:23:50,030
Help me save my planet.

1102
01:23:51,200 --> 01:23:52,389
Don't give in to fear.

1103
01:23:52,720 --> 01:23:55,350
Fight it. Fight it with me.

1104
01:23:56,920 --> 01:23:58,920
GUARDIAN: Your words are compelling,
young human.

1105
01:23:59,360 --> 01:24:02,450
But as immortals, we must measure
our actions over billions of years...

1106
01:24:03,040 --> 01:24:04,860
..and the fate of the universe.

1107
01:24:05,280 --> 01:24:09,070
We simply cannot risk losing everything
on the chance you might be right.

1108
01:24:09,760 --> 01:24:12,390
Then don't. Don't risk any more lives.

1109
01:24:13,920 --> 01:24:14,860
Just mine.

1110
01:24:16,720 --> 01:24:18,190
Let me go fight for my world...

1111
01:24:18,560 --> 01:24:22,110
.and I'll show you
that will is stronger than fear.

1112
01:24:23,520 --> 01:24:25,340
There is no way you can succeed.

1113
01:24:25,760 --> 01:24:27,620
You will die, Hal Jordan.

1114
01:24:29,440 --> 01:24:31,330
Then I'll die trying.

1115
01:24:34,080 --> 01:24:35,900
Good luck, Green Lantern.

1116
01:24:47,520 --> 01:24:48,640
[RING BEEPING]

1117
01:25:33,080 --> 01:25:34,380
I wouldn't do that.

1118
01:25:37,440 --> 01:25:38,559
Look closely.

1119
01:25:43,480 --> 01:25:44,990
She's beautiful, isn't she?

1120
01:25:46,400 --> 01:25:48,790
I loved her from the moment
I first saw her.

1121
01:25:49,280 --> 01:25:51,950
But she could never see me,
as you were always standing in the way.

1122
01:25:52,480 --> 01:25:54,019
But not anymore.

1123
01:25:54,840 --> 01:25:56,940
No! No! Don't! Don't do this, Hector.

1124
01:25:57,400 --> 01:25:58,700
Please.

1125
01:25:59,520 --> 01:26:00,640
Please.

1126
01:26:01,840 --> 01:26:02,710
I know how you feel.

1127
01:26:03,000 --> 01:26:04,440
[SCOFFS]

1128
01:26:04,800 --> 01:26:06,480
Come on, look at yourself!

1129
01:26:09,280 --> 01:26:11,099
No, I know what it's like...

1130
01:26:12,640 --> 01:26:14,180
..to not live up to expectations...

1131
01:26:14,560 --> 01:26:17,300
..to feel like nothing that you do
will ever be good enough.

1132
01:26:21,760 --> 01:26:23,720
I know what it's like to be afraid.

1133
01:26:25,080 --> 01:26:26,590
Let me help you.

1134
01:26:28,120 --> 01:26:30,540
Hal. You've changed.

1135
01:26:32,080 --> 01:26:35,030
How wonderful that all it took for you
to grow up was the end of the world.

1136
01:26:36,880 --> 01:26:38,320
Now it's my turn.

1137
01:26:40,600 --> 01:26:43,270
And if I can't be like you,
I'm gonna make her like me.

1138
01:26:43,800 --> 01:26:45,620
And let's face it, once she's like me...

1139
01:26:46,640 --> 01:26:48,460
..then you wouldn't be
very interested.

1140
01:26:48,880 --> 01:26:50,630
Hmm? Now, would you?

1141
01:26:52,640 --> 01:26:54,430
-Why can't you?
-Hmm?

1142
01:26:56,000 --> 01:26:57,510
Why can't you be like me?

1143
01:26:57,880 --> 01:26:59,600
Heh. Huh?

1144
01:27:01,040 --> 01:27:02,200
Let her go...

1145
01:27:05,600 --> 01:27:06,540
..and you can have it.

1146
01:27:12,160 --> 01:27:13,700
You can do anything.

1147
01:27:14,560 --> 01:27:15,960
Be anything.

1148
01:27:18,720 --> 01:27:19,910
Take it.

1149
01:27:23,240 --> 01:27:25,130
Let her make the choice.

1150
01:27:30,680 --> 01:27:31,910
Okay.

1151
01:27:48,440 --> 01:27:50,440
[HECTOR GASPING]

1152
01:27:58,560 --> 01:27:59,680
Wow.

1153
01:28:03,200 --> 01:28:05,370
[LAUGHING]

1154
01:28:10,040 --> 01:28:11,200
Now bring her down.

1155
01:28:12,280 --> 01:28:13,440
[SIGHS]

1156
01:28:14,880 --> 01:28:15,860
Hal.

1157
01:28:17,720 --> 01:28:18,590
I lied.

1158
01:28:24,560 --> 01:28:25,860
I lied too.

1159
01:28:26,720 --> 01:28:28,400
See, the way it works is...

1160
01:28:28,800 --> 01:28:29,850
..you have to be chosen.

1161
01:28:31,200 --> 01:28:32,460
[SCREAMS]

1162
01:28:32,800 --> 01:28:35,260
[GRUNTING]

1163
01:28:39,040 --> 01:28:40,160
[BOTH GRUNT]

1164
01:28:46,680 --> 01:28:47,940
[GASPS]

1165
01:28:48,280 --> 01:28:50,280
[ROARING]

1166
01:28:54,160 --> 01:28:55,980
[SCREAMING]

1167
01:29:09,080 --> 01:29:10,730
You have failed me.

1168
01:29:11,120 --> 01:29:13,650
[HECTOR SCREAMING]

1169
01:29:41,200 --> 01:29:42,250
Stay here.

1170
01:29:42,560 --> 01:29:43,680
No problem.

1171
01:29:48,160 --> 01:29:50,900
[GRUNTING]

1172
01:30:03,280 --> 01:30:05,840
[HAL YELLING]

1173
01:30:10,320 --> 01:30:12,849
Your will is strong,
but not strong enough.

1174
01:30:14,240 --> 01:30:16,630
You are nothing without the ring.

1175
01:30:17,120 --> 01:30:18,309
[HAL YELLING]

1176
01:30:25,520 --> 01:30:27,690
[PARALLAX ROARS]

1177
01:30:41,560 --> 01:30:43,840
POLICEMAN [OVER LOUDSPEAKER]:
You must move out of the area now.

1178
01:30:44,320 --> 01:30:46,420
Please clear the streets.

1179
01:30:46,880 --> 01:30:48,390
Clear the streets immediately.

1180
01:30:51,920 --> 01:30:53,810
You can never beat this. You'll die.

1181
01:30:54,240 --> 01:30:55,710
At least I can get it away from here.

1182
01:30:56,080 --> 01:30:58,430
-How do you think you're gonna do that?
-I don't know. I don't know.

1183
01:30:58,920 --> 01:30:59,790
[STAMMERS]

1184
01:31:00,080 --> 01:31:02,110
Maybe I can outthink it or....

1185
01:31:02,560 --> 01:31:04,100
The dogfight, remember?

1186
01:31:04,480 --> 01:31:05,740
Those were a couple of jets.

1187
01:31:06,080 --> 01:31:07,870
Unbeatable jets.

1188
01:31:10,320 --> 01:31:12,490
The ring chose me for a reason.

1189
01:31:14,000 --> 01:31:15,510
This is why.

1190
01:31:17,240 --> 01:31:19,660
-Look, I'm probably not--
-Please don't. No.

1191
01:31:20,160 --> 01:31:21,320
Hey.

1192
01:31:21,640 --> 01:31:23,710
[CAROL CRYING]

1193
01:31:30,160 --> 01:31:32,050
POLICEMAN [OVER LOUDSPEAKER]:
This is a mandatory evacuation.

1194
01:31:32,480 --> 01:31:34,440
Everyone must clear the streets
immediately.

1195
01:31:36,240 --> 01:31:39,679
Police emergency,
everyone must clear the street now.

1196
01:31:40,480 --> 01:31:41,849
[CROWD GASPING]

1197
01:31:44,320 --> 01:31:46,849
[CROWD SCREAMING
AND SHOUTING]

1198
01:32:14,000 --> 01:32:16,030
DRIVER:
Everybody off now! Now!

1199
01:32:16,840 --> 01:32:17,890
Go! Go!

1200
01:32:27,000 --> 01:32:28,120
MAN:
Run!

1201
01:32:31,520 --> 01:32:32,780
[DRIVER SCREAMS]

1202
01:32:37,280 --> 01:32:38,400
[SCREAMS]

1203
01:32:47,280 --> 01:32:48,509
[ROARS]

1204
01:32:51,680 --> 01:32:52,620
[SCREAMS]

1205
01:32:53,760 --> 01:32:55,090
-Run!
-Aah! Aah!

1206
01:32:56,960 --> 01:32:59,420
[GRUNTING]

1207
01:33:03,200 --> 01:33:06,080
[CAR ALARM BLARING]

1208
01:33:07,280 --> 01:33:08,469
[ROARS]

1209
01:33:13,240 --> 01:33:15,519
l feel your fear growing.

1210
01:33:16,240 --> 01:33:17,750
You will be dead soon.

1211
01:33:18,120 --> 01:33:20,470
In brightest day, in blackest night--

1212
01:33:20,960 --> 01:33:23,910
And when you're gone,
I'll destroy everything you ever loved.

1213
01:33:24,480 --> 01:33:27,009
--no evil shall escape my sight.

1214
01:33:27,520 --> 01:33:30,430
Your family, your home,
your planet will be no more.

1215
01:33:31,240 --> 01:33:34,500
Let those who worship evil's might--

1216
01:33:35,120 --> 01:33:39,019
The entire human race will be wiped out
because you, Hal Jordan...

1217
01:33:39,720 --> 01:33:41,020
.. Were afraid.

1218
01:33:41,360 --> 01:33:43,500
--beware my power:

1219
01:33:44,320 --> 01:33:45,440
Green Lantern's light!

1220
01:33:46,240 --> 01:33:49,050
[PARALLAX ROARING]

1221
01:34:58,480 --> 01:35:01,780
The bigger you are,
the faster you burn.

1222
01:35:23,480 --> 01:35:25,019
[ROARING]

1223
01:36:10,240 --> 01:36:11,849
[SCREAMS]

1224
01:36:58,880 --> 01:37:00,950
SINESTRO: Though his time
wearing the ring has been brief...

1225
01:37:02,280 --> 01:37:06,740
..Hal Jordan's defeat of Parallax will be
remembered as long as the Corps exists.

1226
01:37:07,560 --> 01:37:10,610
His actions are a reminder
of why the ring chose each of us.

1227
01:37:12,160 --> 01:37:13,700
To overcome fear...

1228
01:37:14,560 --> 01:37:17,370
.and destroy evil
wherever it may hide.

1229
01:37:25,960 --> 01:37:27,850
As Lanterns,
we must fight with all our will.

1230
01:37:29,800 --> 01:37:31,870
Our wills haven't always been united.

1231
01:37:33,920 --> 01:37:34,970
It's time they were.

1232
01:37:35,680 --> 01:37:36,760
[GRUNTS]

1233
01:37:37,080 --> 01:37:39,290
-Ha-ha-ha.
-Can I train them or can I train them?

1234
01:37:40,800 --> 01:37:42,800
SINESTRO:
You're impertinent, Hal Jordan.

1235
01:37:43,240 --> 01:37:46,290
You're rash, volatile, opinionated.

1236
01:37:48,160 --> 01:37:50,900
It seems Abin Sur found another
just like himself.

1237
01:38:02,720 --> 01:38:05,250
[LANTERNS CHEERING]

1238
01:38:31,520 --> 01:38:33,980
Wow, I am never getting used to that.

1239
01:38:38,720 --> 01:38:41,670
My new job requires that I travel.

1240
01:38:42,520 --> 01:38:43,390
[CHUCKLES]

1241
01:38:44,800 --> 01:38:45,990
Be away for a while.

1242
01:38:49,840 --> 01:38:53,000
Away, never gone.

1243
01:38:58,000 --> 01:38:59,010
Hal.

1244
01:38:59,320 --> 01:39:00,440
Yeah?

1245
01:39:00,960 --> 01:39:02,780
Can you take off the mask?

1246
01:39:08,000 --> 01:39:09,120
That's really cool. Ha, ha.

1247
01:39:20,800 --> 01:39:21,780
[CAROL SIGHS]

1248
01:39:23,360 --> 01:39:24,900
So, what happens now?

1249
01:39:26,320 --> 01:39:27,929
I'm gonna go look for trouble.

1250
01:39:29,840 --> 01:39:31,070
[CAROL CHUCKLES]

1251
01:39:50,680 --> 01:39:52,750
TOMAR-RE: Of aff the Lanterns
who have ever worn the ring...

1252
01:39:53,200 --> 01:39:55,730
..there was one
whose light shined brightest.

1253
01:39:56,480 --> 01:39:59,290
At first, his humanity
was thought to be a weakness.

1254
01:39:59,840 --> 01:40:03,140
And yet it proved to be
his greatest strength.

1255
01:49:16,880 --> 01:49:18,630
[English - US - SDH]

